16
00:00:59,520 --> 00:00:59,840
Wow.

17
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:00,800
Okay, that's insane.

18
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:02,719
I haven't seen numbers like that before.

19
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:06,159
