20
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:11,439
So I followed the bootstrapping movement on X like Peter Levels, all those guys.

21
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:17,759
I was doing actually internships in fang companies but once I got there I realized maybe it's not for me.

22
00:01:17,759 --> 00:01:25,759
I looked at people five 10 years ahead of me in their career and it was not something that I was looking up to but when I saw like people like Peter,

23
00:01:25,759 --> 00:01:31,520
people like Danny Pusma especially in the AI wave I thought hey like I can actually do this.

24
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:37,600
I saw people doing demos of how you can build a chat GBT for your data and stuff like that but no one was building a product around it.

25
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,040
I knew like this is a good idea.

26
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,479
I didn't do any validation or anything.

27
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:43,439
I just like said if I don't do this someone else will.

28
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:46,000
