65
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,799
People need to see your face a lot.

66
00:03:58,799 --> 00:04:01,519
Preferably, if you can do videos, too, post them on X.

67
00:04:01,519 --> 00:04:08,560
a few people in the build and public space are doing that and they're doing very well because not enough people are doing that so you stand out more.

68
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,640
Frame it as like I'm building something.

69
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,159
I'm learning a lot along the way.

70
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:13,599
I'm going to take you on that journey.

71
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:17,199
I would say also an important part is not to be boring.

72
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:19,120
I think it's better to be more personal.

73
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,880
Share like your personal story.

74
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:28,240
Have a personality like have controversial takes maybe if if it's something you actually believe in because that's how you get people to notice you.

75
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:28,800
All right.

