00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:18,880
What have you learned through the process that surprised you?

179
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:19,200
Yeah.

180
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:24,800
So, I think going into it where we assume that there's like a blueprint on how to build a good business.

